  p=11: prod(sin²+sin²m) = 0.9560546875, F_p·p/2^{p-1} = 1.5468750000
    Note: ω^{mk} = ω^{-(m+1)k} since m+(m+1)=p
    k=1: ω^{mk} = -0.959493+0.281733j, ω^{-(m+1)k} = -0.959493+0.281733j, match: True
    k=2: ω^{mk} = 0.841254-0.540641j, ω^{-(m+1)k} = 0.841254-0.540641j, match: True
    k=3: ω^{mk} = -0.654861+0.755750j, ω^{-(m+1)k} = -0.654861+0.755750j, match: True
